graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>Kubeflow]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    NotebookController -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22.0+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    NotebookController -.->|VirtualService CRDs| Istio[Istio Service Mesh]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|consumed by| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    NotebookController -.->|routing integration| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway]

    %% Kubernetes API interactions
    NotebookController -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    K8sAPI -->|RBAC| NotebookController

    %% Managed Resources
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| StatefulSets[StatefulSets]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| Services[Services]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| VirtualServices[VirtualServices<br/>networking.istio.io]

    %% Workload Dependencies
    StatefulSets -->|creates| NotebookPods[Jupyter Notebook Pods]
    Services -->|routes to| NotebookPods

    %% Culling Integration
    NotebookController -->|queries /api/kernels| NotebookPods

    %% Certificate Management
    NotebookController -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]

    %% Monitoring Flow
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes| NotebookController

    %% Istio Flow
    Istio -.->|configures| VirtualServices
    IstioGateway -.->|routes via| VirtualServices

